<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>{{.Meta.Title}}</title>
<style>
  /* ============== Page setup ============== */
  @page {
    size: A4;
    margin: 14mm 12mm 16mm 12mm;
    @bottom-center {
      content: counter(page) " / " counter(pages);
      font-family: "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    @bottom-left {
      content: "矩阵云安全平台 · 漏洞管理专项报告";
      font-family: "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
      font-size: 9px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }
    @bottom-right {
      content: "机密 · 仅限内部使用";
      font-family: "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
      font-size: 9px;
      color: #dc2626;
    }
  }
  @page :first {
    margin: 0;
    @bottom-center { content: none; }
    @bottom-left { content: none; }
    @bottom-right { content: none; }
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; }

  html, body {
    margin: 0; padding: 0;
    font-family: "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #1f2937;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
    print-color-adjust: exact;
  }

  /* ============== Cover ============== */
  .cover {
    width: 100vw;
    height: 100vh;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 28mm 22mm 24mm 22mm;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at top right, rgba(114,46,209,0.07) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom left, rgba(37,99,235,0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
      #ffffff;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto;
    row-gap: 0;
    page-break-after: always;
    position: relative;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cover-meta { align-self: end; }
  .cover::before {
    content: ""; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #2563eb 0%, #722ed1 100%);
  }
  .cover-brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 18px; }
  .cover-brand img { width: 64px; height: 64px; }
  .cover-brand-name {
    font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: #1f2937; line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }
  .cover-brand-en {
    font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", Consolas, monospace; margin-top: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .cover-mid {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center;
    min-height: 0;
  }
  .cover-kind {
    font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 10px; color: #2563eb;
    font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .cover-title {
    font-size: 60px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #722ed1 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
    margin: 0 0 30px 0;
  }
  .cover-period {
    font-size: 19px; color: #374151;
    padding: 10px 28px; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 999px;
    background: #ffffff;
  }
  .cover-deco {
    margin-top: 22px;
    width: 240px; height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #2563eb, #722ed1, transparent);
  }

  /* 亮点四列 */
  .cover-highlights {
    margin-top: 36px;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 14px;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .cover-highlights .hl {
    padding: 14px 10px;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-top: 3px solid #2563eb;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: #ffffff;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  }
  .cover-highlights .hl.hl-c { border-top-color: #dc2626; }
  .cover-highlights .hl.hl-b { border-top-color: #ea580c; }
  .cover-highlights .hl.hl-p { border-top-color: #722ed1; }
  .cover-highlights .hl.hl-g { border-top-color: #22c55e; }
  .cover-highlights .hl-num {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; color: #111827;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px; line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .cover-highlights .hl-lbl {
    font-size: 11.5px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 4px;
  }

  /* 本期摘要 */
  .cover-summary {
    margin-top: 28px;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(37,99,235,0.04) 0%, transparent 100%);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .cover-summary-title {
    font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #2563eb;
    margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 2px;
  }
  .cover-summary-text {
    font-size: 14px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.9;
    text-align: justify;
  }

  .cover-meta {
    border-top: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
    padding-top: 22px;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 10px 40px;
    font-size: 14.5px;
  }
  .cover-meta-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; }
  .cover-meta-label { color: #6b7280; }
  .cover-meta-value { font-family: "JetBrains Mono", Consolas, monospace; font-weight: 500; color: #111827; }
  .cover-class {
    grid-column: span 2; margin-top: 16px; text-align: center;
    color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 5px;
    font-size: 15px;
    padding: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.2);
    background: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.04);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  /* ============== Page ============== */
  .page {
    padding: 0 2mm;
  }
  .force-break { page-break-before: always; break-before: page; }

  /* TOC */
  .toc.page {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    padding: 12mm 12mm 14mm 12mm;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  }
  .toc h2 { text-align: center; letter-spacing: 16px; font-size: 30px; margin: 0 0 6mm 0; color: #1f2937; }
  .toc .toc-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; counter-reset: toc; max-width: 170mm; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 100%; }
  .toc .toc-list > li {
    counter-increment: toc;
    display: flex; align-items: baseline;
    padding: 6px 0; border-bottom: 1px dotted #d1d5db;
    font-size: 15.5px;
  }
  .toc .toc-list > li::before {
    content: counter(toc) ".";
    color: #2563eb; font-family: "JetBrains Mono", Consolas, monospace;
    font-weight: 600; min-width: 32px; font-size: 16px;
  }
  .toc-title { flex: 1; }
  .toc-page { color: #6b7280; font-family: "JetBrains Mono", Consolas, monospace; font-size: 14px; }
  .toc-hint {
    margin: 4mm auto 0; max-width: 170mm; padding: 10px 14px;
    background: #f9fafb; border-left: 3px solid #2563eb;
    font-size: 12.5px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .toc-extra { max-width: 170mm; margin: 5mm auto 0; width: 100%; }
  .toc-block { margin-bottom: 5mm; }
  .toc-block-title {
    font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #1f2937;
    margin-bottom: 6px; padding-left: 10px;
    border-left: 3px solid #722ed1;
  }
  .toc-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13.5px; }
  .toc-table td {
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
  }
  .toc-table td:first-child {
    width: 28%; color: #6b7280; font-weight: 500;
  }
  .toc-table td:last-child { color: #111827; }
  .toc-guide { margin: 0; padding-left: 22px; font-size: 13.5px; line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
  .toc-guide li { margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .toc-guide b { color: #2563eb; }
  .toc-footer {
    margin-top: auto; padding-top: 8px;
    border-top: 1px dashed #d1d5db;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 11.5px; color: #9ca3af;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  }

  /* Section heading */
  h2.sec {
    font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600;
    margin: 18px 0 12px 0; padding-bottom: 7px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #2563eb;
    page-break-after: avoid;
    break-after: avoid;
    color: #1f2937;
  }
  h2.sec:first-of-type { margin-top: 6px; }
  h2.sec + p,
  h2.sec + .stat-row,
  h2.sec + table.t,
  h2.sec + .fig,
  h2.sec + h3.subsec,
  h2.sec + ul,
  h2.sec + ol {
    page-break-before: avoid;
    break-before: avoid;
  }
  h3.subsec {
    font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600;
    margin: 16px 0 9px 0; padding-left: 11px;
    border-left: 4px solid #722ed1;
    page-break-after: avoid;
    break-after: avoid;
    color: #1f2937;
  }
  h3.subsec + table.t,
  h3.subsec + p,
  h3.subsec + .fig {
    page-break-before: avoid;
    break-before: avoid;
  }
  p { margin: 0 0 12px 0; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.85; font-size: 14.5px; }
  p.no-indent { text-indent: 0; }
  ul, ol { margin: 6px 0 14px 0; padding-left: 26px; font-size: 14.5px; line-height: 1.9; }
  ul li, ol li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  b, strong { color: #111827; font-weight: 600; }

  /* Tables */
  table.t {
    width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13.5px;
    margin: 8px 0 14px 0;
  }
  table.t thead th {
    background: #f3f4f6; color: #111827;
    text-align: left; padding: 9px 12px;
    border-top: 1px solid #d1d5db;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #2563eb;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  table.t tbody td {
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  table.t tbody tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #fafafa; }
  table.t tr { page-break-inside: avoid; }
  td.num, th.num { text-align: right; font-family: "JetBrains Mono", Consolas, monospace; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  td.code { font-family: "JetBrains Mono", Consolas, monospace; font-size: 12.5px; word-break: break-all; }
  td.empty { text-align: center; color: #9ca3af; font-style: italic; padding: 16px; }

  .sev-pill { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 9px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; }
  .sev-dot { display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 7px; vertical-align: middle; }

  .row2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 18px; margin: 8px 0 10px 0; }
  .row2 > * { min-width: 0; }
  .row2 h3.subsec:first-of-type { margin-top: 0; }
  .row1 { display: block; margin: 8px 0 10px 0; }

  .fig { margin: 10px 0 14px 0; page-break-inside: avoid; text-align: center; }
  .fig svg { max-width: 100%; height: auto; }
  .fig-cap { margin-top: 4px; font-size: 13px; color: #4b5563; letter-spacing: 1px; }

  .empty-block { color: #9ca3af; font-style: italic; padding: 12px 0; font-size: 14px; }

  .stat-row {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 10px;
    margin: 10px 0 14px 0;
  }
  .stat-row .cell {
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
    padding: 12px 14px; border-radius: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fbfcfe 0%, #ffffff 100%);
  }
  .stat-row .cell-label { font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; }
  .stat-row .cell-value {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .stat-row .cell.sev-c { border-left-color: #dc2626; }
  .stat-row .cell.sev-h { border-left-color: #ea580c; }
  .stat-row .cell.sev-m { border-left-color: #ca8a04; }
  .stat-row .cell.sev-l { border-left-color: #0891b2; }
  .stat-row .cell.brand { border-left-color: #722ed1; }
  .stat-row .cell.good { border-left-color: #22c55e; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ============== Cover (page 1) ============== -->
<section class="cover">
  <div class="cover-brand">
    {{if .Assets.LogoURI}}
    <img src="{{.Assets.LogoURI}}" alt="logo"/>
    {{end}}
    <div>
      <div class="cover-brand-name">矩阵云安全平台</div>
      <div class="cover-brand-en">MxCwpp Security Platform</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cover-mid">
    <div class="cover-kind">漏洞管理与修复</div>
    <h1 class="cover-title">专项分析报告</h1>
    <div class="cover-period">{{.Meta.Period}}</div>
    <div class="cover-deco"></div>

    <div class="cover-highlights">
      <div class="hl"><div class="hl-num">{{.Summary.TotalVulns}}</div><div class="hl-lbl">CVE 总数</div></div>
      <div class="hl hl-c"><div class="hl-num">{{.Summary.CriticalVulns}}</div><div class="hl-lbl">严重 CVE</div></div>
      <div class="hl hl-b"><div class="hl-num">{{.Summary.AffectedHosts}}</div><div class="hl-lbl">受影响主机</div></div>
      <div class="hl hl-g"><div class="hl-num">{{.Summary.FixedVulns}}</div><div class="hl-lbl">已修复</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="cover-summary">
      <div class="cover-summary-title">本期摘要</div>
      <div class="cover-summary-text">
        平台基于 <b>{{.Meta.EnabledSources}}</b> 个启用情报源共聚合披露 CVE <b>{{.Summary.TotalVulns}}</b> 个；
        其中严重 <b>{{.Summary.CriticalVulns}}</b> 个 / 高危 <b>{{.Summary.HighVulns}}</b> 个，
        影响主机 <b>{{.Summary.AffectedHosts}}</b> 台；
        累计修复 <b>{{.Summary.FixedVulns}}</b> 个（修复率 <b>{{printf "%.1f" .Derived.FixRate}}%</b>），
        仍待修复 <b>{{.Summary.UnpatchedVulns}}</b> 个、已忽略 <b>{{.Summary.IgnoredVulns}}</b> 个。
        整体漏洞态势<b>{{.Posture.Descriptor}}</b>。
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cover-meta">
    <div class="cover-meta-row"><span class="cover-meta-label">报告编号</span><span class="cover-meta-value">{{.Meta.ReportID}}</span></div>
    <div class="cover-meta-row"><span class="cover-meta-label">生成时间</span><span class="cover-meta-value">{{.Meta.GeneratedAt}}</span></div>
    <div class="cover-meta-row"><span class="cover-meta-label">报告周期</span><span class="cover-meta-value">{{.Meta.Period}}</span></div>
    <div class="cover-meta-row"><span class="cover-meta-label">受影响主机</span><span class="cover-meta-value">{{.Summary.AffectedHosts}} 台</span></div>
    <div class="cover-meta-row"><span class="cover-meta-label">情报源</span><span class="cover-meta-value">{{.Meta.EnabledSources}} / {{.Meta.TotalSources}} 启用</span></div>
    <div class="cover-meta-row"><span class="cover-meta-label">渲染引擎</span><span class="cover-meta-value">Gotenberg + Chromium</span></div>
    <div class="cover-class">机　密 · 仅 限 内 部 使 用</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============== TOC (page 2) ============== -->
<section class="page toc force-break">
  <h2>目　录</h2>
  <ol class="toc-list">
    <li><span class="toc-title">执行摘要</span><span class="toc-page">03</span></li>
    <li><span class="toc-title">关键指标概览（CVE 总览 / 严重度 / 主机覆盖 / 修复率）</span><span class="toc-page">04</span></li>
    <li><span class="toc-title">严重程度分布</span><span class="toc-page">05</span></li>
    <li><span class="toc-title">Top 10 高危 CVE 清单</span><span class="toc-page">06</span></li>
    <li><span class="toc-title">受影响主机 Top 10</span><span class="toc-page">07</span></li>
    <li><span class="toc-title">修复进度统计</span><span class="toc-page">08</span></li>
    <li><span class="toc-title">SLA 达成情况（按严重程度分桶）</span><span class="toc-page">09</span></li>
    <li><span class="toc-title">CVE 情报源覆盖</span><span class="toc-page">10</span></li>
    <li><span class="toc-title">改进建议与附录</span><span class="toc-page">11</span></li>
  </ol>
  <div class="toc-extra">
    <div class="toc-block">
      <div class="toc-block-title">数据范围</div>
      <table class="toc-table">
        <tr><td>报告周期</td><td>{{.Meta.Period}}</td></tr>
        <tr><td>主机覆盖</td><td>{{.Summary.AffectedHosts}} 台受影响 · 在线 {{.Meta.OnlineHosts}} 台</td></tr>
        <tr><td>情报源</td><td>{{.Meta.EnabledSources}} / {{.Meta.TotalSources}} 启用（NVD / OSV / RHSA / CNNVD / CNVD 等）</td></tr>
        <tr><td>CVE / 修复</td><td>{{.Summary.TotalVulns}} 个披露 · {{.Summary.FixedVulns}} 个已修复（{{printf "%.1f" .Derived.FixRate}}%）</td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="toc-footer">
      © 矩阵云安全 · MxCwpp Security Platform　|　报告引擎 v1.0　|　所有数据为实时观测，未经任何人工修饰
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============== §1 执行摘要 ============== -->
<section class="page force-break">
  <h2 class="sec">1. 执行摘要</h2>
  <p>
    本报告覆盖 <b>{{.Meta.Period}}</b>，对接入矩阵云安全平台的 <b>{{.Meta.OnlineHosts}}</b> 台主机的漏洞管理数据进行统计分析。
    报告期内，平台基于 <b>{{.Meta.EnabledSources}}</b> 个启用情报源共披露 CVE
    <b>{{.Summary.TotalVulns}}</b> 个（严重 <b>{{.Summary.CriticalVulns}}</b> · 高危 <b>{{.Summary.HighVulns}}</b> ·
    中危 <b>{{.Summary.MediumVulns}}</b> · 低危 <b>{{.Summary.LowVulns}}</b>），
    影响主机 <b>{{.Summary.AffectedHosts}}</b> 台；累计修复 <b>{{.Summary.FixedVulns}}</b> 个
    （修复率 <b>{{printf "%.1f" .Derived.FixRate}}%</b>），仍待修复 <b>{{.Summary.UnpatchedVulns}}</b> 个。
    整体漏洞态势<b>{{.Posture.Descriptor}}</b>。
  </p>

  <h3 class="subsec">核心结论</h3>
  <ul>
    {{range .Conclusions}}<li>{{.}}</li>{{end}}
  </ul>

  <h2 class="sec">2. 关键指标概览</h2>

  <div class="stat-row">
    <div class="cell good"><div class="cell-label">在线主机</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Meta.OnlineHosts}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell brand"><div class="cell-label">CVE 总数</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Summary.TotalVulns}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell sev-c"><div class="cell-label">严重 CVE</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Summary.CriticalVulns}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell sev-h"><div class="cell-label">高危 CVE</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Summary.HighVulns}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">受影响主机</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Summary.AffectedHosts}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell good"><div class="cell-label">已修复</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Summary.FixedVulns}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell sev-m"><div class="cell-label">待修复</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Summary.UnpatchedVulns}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">已忽略</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Summary.IgnoredVulns}}</div></div>
  </div>

  <table class="t">
    <thead><tr><th style="width:30%">指标</th><th style="width:25%" class="num">本周期</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>修复率</td><td class="num">{{printf "%.1f" .Derived.FixRate}}%</td><td>已修复 / CVE 总数</td></tr>
      <tr><td>主机覆盖率</td><td class="num">{{printf "%.1f" .Derived.HostCoverage}}%</td><td>受影响主机 / 在线主机</td></tr>
      <tr><td>情报源启用率</td><td class="num">{{printf "%.1f" .Derived.SourceEnableRate}}%</td><td>已启用 / 平台情报源总数</td></tr>
      <tr><td>带可利用代码</td><td class="num">{{.Summary.WithExploit}}</td><td>HasExploit=true，需优先处置</td></tr>
      <tr><td>KEV 名录命中</td><td class="num">{{.Summary.InKEV}}</td><td>CISA Known Exploited Vulnerabilities</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<!-- ============== §3 严重程度分布 ============== -->
<section class="page">
  <h2 class="sec">3. 严重程度分布</h2>
  <p>本周期披露的 CVE 按 CVSS 严重程度的分布。严重 / 高危占比直接决定整改优先级与 SLA 时长。</p>

  <div class="fig">
    {{.Charts.SeverityPie}}
    <div class="fig-cap">图 3-1　CVE 严重程度分布</div>
  </div>

  <table class="t">
    <thead><tr><th>严重程度</th><th class="num" style="width:120px">数量</th><th class="num" style="width:120px">占比</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      {{range .SeverityRows}}
      <tr>
        <td><span class="sev-dot" style="background:{{.Color}}"></span>{{.Label}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{.Count}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{printf "%.1f" .Pct}}%</td>
      </tr>
      {{end}}
    </tbody>
  </table>

  {{if .Charts.ComponentBar}}
  <div class="fig">
    {{.Charts.ComponentBar}}
    <div class="fig-cap">图 3-2　Top 10 受影响组件（按 CVE 数）</div>
  </div>
  {{end}}
</section>

<!-- ============== §4 Top 10 高危 CVE ============== -->
<section class="page">
  <h2 class="sec">4. Top 10 高危 CVE 清单</h2>
  <p>按 CVSS 评分降序，含可利用代码 / KEV 命中标记。建议安全团队 24h 内对严重 + 已剥削项启动应急响应流程。</p>

  <table class="t">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:24px">#</th>
        <th style="width:130px">CVE</th>
        <th style="width:60px">级别</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:55px">CVSS</th>
        <th>组件</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:60px">主机</th>
        <th style="width:90px">标记</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {{range $i, $v := .TopVulns}}
      <tr>
        <td>{{add $i 1}}</td>
        <td class="code">{{$v.CveID}}</td>
        <td><span class="sev-pill" style="background:{{$v.BgColor}};color:{{$v.Color}}">{{$v.Label}}</span></td>
        <td class="num">{{printf "%.1f" $v.CvssScore}}</td>
        <td>{{$v.Component}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{$v.AffectedHosts}}</td>
        <td>{{$v.Tags}}</td>
      </tr>
      {{else}}
      <tr><td class="empty" colspan="7">本周期无披露 CVE</td></tr>
      {{end}}
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<!-- ============== §5 受影响主机 Top 10 ============== -->
<section class="page">
  <h2 class="sec">5. 受影响主机 Top 10</h2>
  <p>按主机所含 CVE 数降序排列，含严重 / 高危分布。多严重 CVE 集中主机建议优先纳入修复计划或临时网络隔离。</p>

  <table class="t">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:24px">#</th>
        <th>主机</th>
        <th>IP</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:70px">CVE 数</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:60px">严重</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:60px">高危</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {{range $i, $h := .TopHosts}}
      <tr>
        <td>{{add $i 1}}</td>
        <td>{{$h.Hostname}}</td>
        <td class="code">{{$h.IP}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{$h.VulnCount}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{$h.CriticalCount}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{$h.HighCount}}</td>
      </tr>
      {{else}}
      <tr><td class="empty" colspan="6">本周期无主机受影响</td></tr>
      {{end}}
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<!-- ============== §6 修复进度统计 ============== -->
<section class="page">
  <h2 class="sec">6. 修复进度统计</h2>
  <p>
    本周期共发起修复任务 <b>{{.Fix.TotalTasks}}</b> 次，其中成功 <b>{{.Fix.SuccessTasks}}</b> 次、
    失败 <b>{{.Fix.FailedTasks}}</b> 次、进行中 <b>{{.Fix.RunningTasks}}</b> 次、
    待人工确认 <b>{{.Fix.PendingVerifyTasks}}</b> 次。
    任务成功率 <b>{{printf "%.1f" .Fix.SuccessRate}}%</b>。
  </p>

  <div class="stat-row">
    <div class="cell brand"><div class="cell-label">修复任务总数</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Fix.TotalTasks}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell good"><div class="cell-label">成功</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Fix.SuccessTasks}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell sev-c"><div class="cell-label">失败</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Fix.FailedTasks}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell sev-m"><div class="cell-label">待确认</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Fix.PendingVerifyTasks}}</div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="fig">
    {{.Charts.FixStatusBar}}
    <div class="fig-cap">图 6-1　CVE 修复状态（已修复 vs 待修复 vs 已忽略）</div>
  </div>

  <table class="t">
    <thead><tr><th>状态</th><th class="num" style="width:120px">数量</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>已修复 (fixed)</td><td class="num">{{.Summary.FixedVulns}}</td><td>补丁已落地，pre-check 复测通过</td></tr>
      <tr><td>待修复 (unpatched)</td><td class="num">{{.Summary.UnpatchedVulns}}</td><td>影响仍存在，需安排修复任务</td></tr>
      <tr><td>已忽略 (ignored)</td><td class="num">{{.Summary.IgnoredVulns}}</td><td>已研判可豁免（误报 / 无攻击面 / 接受风险）</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<!-- ============== §7 SLA 达成情况 ============== -->
<section class="page">
  <h2 class="sec">7. SLA 达成情况</h2>
  <p>
    按严重程度分桶统计修复 SLA：严重 <b>24h</b> / 高危 <b>72h</b> / 中危 <b>14d</b> / 低危 <b>30d</b>。
    分子为发现至修复完成时长 ≤ SLA 的 CVE 数，分母为该严重程度下已结案 CVE 数。
  </p>

  <table class="t">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>严重程度</th>
        <th style="width:90px">SLA</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:90px">达成</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:90px">总计</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:90px">达成率</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {{range .SLARows}}
      <tr>
        <td><span class="sev-dot" style="background:{{.Color}}"></span>{{.Label}}</td>
        <td>{{.Window}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{.Met}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{.Total}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{printf "%.1f" .Rate}}%</td>
      </tr>
      {{end}}
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p class="no-indent" style="margin-top:8px;color:#6b7280;font-size:13px;">
    注：仅统计 status = fixed 且 patched_at 不为空的 CVE。从 discovered_at 到 patched_at 计算实际耗时。
  </p>
</section>

<!-- ============== §8 CVE 情报源覆盖 ============== -->
<section class="page">
  <h2 class="sec">8. CVE 情报源覆盖</h2>
  <p>
    本平台 <b>{{.Meta.EnabledSources}} / {{.Meta.TotalSources}}</b> 个情报源启用。
    全球源含 NVD / OSV / RHSA / USN / Debian Security Tracker / Alpine SecDB，
    国内合规源含 CNNVD / CNVD（国家信息安全漏洞库），
    剥削情报源含 CISA KEV / exploit-db。
    多源融合可提升 CVE 覆盖完整度并避免单点失效。
  </p>

  <h3 class="subsec">8.1　情报源状态总览</h3>
  <table class="t">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:24px">#</th>
        <th>情报源</th>
        <th style="width:60px">区域</th>
        <th style="width:110px">分类</th>
        <th style="width:70px">状态</th>
        <th style="width:130px">最近同步</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:80px">入库 CVE</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {{range $i, $s := .Sources}}
      <tr>
        <td>{{add $i 1}}</td>
        <td>{{$s.DisplayName}}</td>
        <td>{{$s.Region}}</td>
        <td>{{$s.Category}}</td>
        <td>{{if $s.Enabled}}<span class="sev-pill" style="background:#dcfce7;color:#16a34a">启用</span>{{else}}<span class="sev-pill" style="background:#f3f4f6;color:#6b7280">禁用</span>{{end}}</td>
        <td>{{$s.LastSyncAt}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{$s.LastCount}}</td>
      </tr>
      {{else}}
      <tr><td class="empty" colspan="7">未配置情报源</td></tr>
      {{end}}
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3 class="subsec">8.2　CVE 来源分布</h3>
  <table class="t">
    <thead><tr><th>来源</th><th class="num" style="width:120px">CVE 数</th><th class="num" style="width:120px">占比</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      {{range .SourceDist}}
      <tr>
        <td>{{.Label}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{.Count}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{printf "%.1f" .Pct}}%</td>
      </tr>
      {{else}}
      <tr><td class="empty" colspan="3">无来源标记</td></tr>
      {{end}}
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<!-- ============== §9 改进建议 + 附录 ============== -->
<section class="page">
  <h2 class="sec">9. 改进建议</h2>
  <p>基于本周期数据，平台自动生成如下改进建议供安全运营与运维团队参考：</p>
  <ol>
    {{range .Improvements}}<li>{{.}}</li>{{else}}<li>本周期未生成自动建议（数据样本较小或修复进度健康）。</li>{{end}}
  </ol>

  <h3 class="subsec">附录 A　报告说明</h3>
  <table class="t">
    <tbody>
      <tr><td style="width:30%">数据来源</td><td>ClickHouse 集群（vulnerabilities / host_vulnerabilities 漏洞库 + 主机关联）+ MySQL（remediation_tasks / vuln_data_sources / hosts 元配置）</td></tr>
      <tr><td>生成方式</td><td>矩阵云安全平台服务端 Go html/template 渲染，自动生成无人工调整</td></tr>
      <tr><td>图表渲染</td><td>服务端 SVG 手绘，矢量化、可缩放、PDF 中保持清晰</td></tr>
      <tr><td>PDF 引擎</td><td>Chromium Headless（Gotenberg HTML→PDF），文本可搜索、可复制、可粘贴</td></tr>
      <tr><td>报告编号</td><td>{{.Meta.ReportID}}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>生成时间</td><td>{{.Meta.GeneratedAt}}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>密级</td><td>机密 · 仅限内部使用 · 不得转发至非授权人员</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3 class="subsec">附录 B　术语对照</h3>
  <table class="t">
    <thead><tr><th style="width:25%">术语</th><th>定义</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>CVE</td><td>Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures，业界通用漏洞编号</td></tr>
      <tr><td>CVSS</td><td>Common Vulnerability Scoring System，漏洞评分体系，0-10 分</td></tr>
      <tr><td>KEV</td><td>CISA Known Exploited Vulnerabilities 已剥削漏洞名录</td></tr>
      <tr><td>EPSS</td><td>Exploit Prediction Scoring System 利用预测评分</td></tr>
      <tr><td>修复率</td><td>已修复 CVE / CVE 总数，反映安全运营对接闭环效率</td></tr>
      <tr><td>SLA</td><td>Service Level Agreement，按严重程度约定的修复时限</td></tr>
      <tr><td>情报源</td><td>聚合的上游 CVE 数据来源（NVD / OSV / RHSA / CNNVD 等）</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

</body>
</html>
